description: Old soldiers may fade away, but so do young mutants! On the verge of disintegration, Kitty Pryde seems resigned to her doom — but the X-Men will do anything to save her, even bargain with a worse doom...DOCTOR Doom! What stunning secret prevents Mister Fantastic and the Fantastic Four from saving the day instead? Is he terrified of failing because his greatest failure, the fateful rocket flight, might have really been his greatest success? Do the answers all come down to wunderkind Franklin Richards? Plus: the classic tale of the two teams' original face-off in Marvel's early era! Collecting FANTASTIC FOUR VS. THE X-MEN #1-4 and FANTASTIC FOUR #28.
name: X-Men vs. Fantastic Four

description: Not many are so pure of heart that they would protect a piece of scum mobster, but Nightwing is one of those few people that will. New to Bludhaven, Dick Grayson is scoping out the city to see what he will be dealing with in the times to come. Bludhaven is a rough town, but Dick is confident that he can clean the place up and make Bruce proud. Read and find out what happens in this exciting series opener!
name: The Breaks

description:
Julie Martin channels the other woman living inside her to break into HeNRI's top-secret research facility and steal the rest of the Beta Suit. But what they find is more than they could have imagined - and far more deadly!

In a bar Will's lab assistant Vijay is out with his friends when he gets a text that Will committed suicide. His friend half jokes that he is next as everyone on the Phi project is dying. He goes to the bathroom and Cain enters the bar looking for him. In the toilets Cain kills another man mistaking him for Vijay who escapes.

Ivy chats with Julie and has her tell her everything. Ivy asks her about Annie and has an idea of how to communicate directly with her. She gets behind Julie and starts to strangle her. She says if she is this close if the suit were to attack it would kill them both so if she can get Julie to blackout it should bring Annie out and it appears to start working.

Meanwhile Hong recovers enough to escape his room.

Will Allison brings you the darkly comic tale of Lonely Bunny, the last bunny in Bunny Town. Join her as she tries to get along with all her predatory friends Malibu the Shark, Blacksie the Cat and Nummy Gator, in the adorably horrible place that is Bunny Town!
The continuing nightmare that is Lonely Bunny's life in the most adorably horrible place on earth - Bunny Town!
name: Living In Bunny Town
